FUNCTION rescale_to_unit(numbers)
    LET min_val <- numbers[1]
    LET max_val <- numbers[1]
    FOR num IN numbers
        min_val <- IF num < min_val THEN num ELSE min_val
        max_val <- IF num > max_val THEN num ELSE max_val
    END FOR
    LET range <- max_val - min_val
    FUNCTION normalize(index)
        IF index = LENGTH(numbers) THEN RETURN []
        LET scaled <- (numbers[index] - min_val) / range
        RETURN [scaled] + normalize(index + 1)
    END FUNCTION
    RETURN normalize(1)
END FUNCTION
